#NewSong2025 #NewHindiSong #RomanticSong #EmraanHashmi #YamiGautam #EmraanYami #HindiSong #HindiNewSong #NewRomanticSong #NewHindiSong2025 #EmraanHashmiNewSong #YamiGautamNewSong #RomanticSongHindi #HindiSong2025 #BetaabDil #SaritDutta

â€œBetaab Dilâ€ is a heart-touching romantic Hindi song that brings back the golden era of 90s Bollywood music. Sung and composed by Sarit Dutta, this soulful melody beautifully captures the emotions of love, longing, and separation. The heartfelt lyrics by Dr. Uma Naveen Mehta paint a timeless picture of a betaab (restless) heart waiting for its beloved.

If you miss the charm of classic love songs, â€œBetaab Dilâ€ will take you straight back to that nostalgic era of melody and emotion.

ðŸŽ§ Experience â€œBetaab Dilâ€ â€” A Pure Hindi Romantic Love Song
Close your eyes, feel the rhythm, and let this song remind you of the beautiful simplicity of true love. Perfect for anyone who believes in eternal romance and misses the soulful tunes of the 90s

ðŸ‘‰ Donâ€™t forget to LIKE, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more soulful music.

Subscribe : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWj7oD9SuDcGciiBQT9BQuw?sub_confirmation=1
__________________________________________________

Song Credits
Song : Betaab Dil
Singer : Sarit Dutta
Music Composer : Sarit Dutta
Lyrics : Dr Uma Naveen Mehta
Backing Vocals : Subhajit Das
Music Produced, Mixed & Mastered by Sarit Dutta @ Rivertone Studio
__________________________________________________

Lyrics:-

Hum chahe itna hi 
Ab tera saath ho
Kya tune kabhi ye jana
Kitna dard hai mujhko

Bekhudi mein chal pade hai
Khudko hi ab mitane
Mere kadam rukte nahi 
Teri galiyon me aane se

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

Baaton ne teri
Mujhko saari raat jagaya
Sanson ne teri
Mujhko yu apna banaya

Koi lamha nahi hai mera
Jisme tu nazar na aaya
Na hamne koi khata ki
fir kyu tune di hai saja

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

Ikk Kudi promises to be more than just a filmâ€”itâ€™s a statement. With strong storytelling and a subject that resonates with todayâ€™s generation, the film is already building buzz across social media. Whether you're a fan of Punjabi cinema or drawn to stories of strength and individuality, Ikk Kudi looks set to leave a mark.

Lyrics for "JISOO - EYES CLOSED"

[Verse 1: JISOO, ZAYN]
Time is standing still and I don't wanna leave your lips
Tracing my body with your fingertips
I know what you're feeling and I know you wanna say it (Yeah, say it)
I do too, but we gotta be patient (Cannot be patient)

[Pre-Chorus: ZAYN, JISOO, JISOO & ZAYN]
'Cause someone like me and someone like you
Really shouldn't work, yeah, the history is proof
Damned if I don't, damned if I do
You know, by now, we've seen it all

[Chorus: JISOO & ZAYN]
Said, oh, we should fall in love with our eyes closed
Better if we keep it where we don't know
The beds we've been in, the namÐµs and the faces of who we wÐµre with
And, oh, ain't nobody perfect, but it's all good
The past can't hurt us if we don't look
Let's let it go, better if we fall in love with our eyes closed

[Post-Chorus: JISOO]
Oh, oh, oh

[Verse 2: JISOO]
I got tunnel vision every second that you're with me
No, I don't care what anybody says, just kiss me (Oh)

[Pre-Chorus: JISOO, ZAYN, JISOO & ZAYN]
'Cause you look like trouble, but it could be good
I've been the same, kind of misunderstood
Whatever you've done, trust, it ain't nothing new
You know by now we've seen it all

[Chorus: JISOO & ZAYN]
Said, oh, we should fall in love with our eyes closed
Better if we keep it where we don't know
The beds we've been in, the names and the faces of who we were with
And, oh, ain't nobody perfect, but it's all good
The past can't hurt us if we don't look
Let's let it go, better if we fall in love with our eyes closed

[Post-Chorus: JISOO]
Oh, oh, oh
Keep your eyes closed

[Pre-Chorus: JISOO, ZAYN, JISOO & ZAYN]
'Cause someone like me and someone like you
Really shouldn't work, yeah, the history is proof
Damned if I don't, damned if I do
You know, by now, we've seen it all

[Chorus: JISOO & ZAYN]
Said, oh, we should fall in love with our eyes closed
Better if we keep it where we don't know
The beds we've been in, the names and the faces of who we were with
And, oh, ain't nobody perfect, but it's all good
The past can't hurt us if we don't look
Let's let it go, better if we fall in love with our eyes closed

[Post-Chorus: JISOO]
Oh, with our eyes closed

Jhin Ta Ta Tata Jhin Ta Ta

Ululululu Myau Mayau

snippet.title: Dayglow - Can I Call You Tonight?
snippet.description:
Dayglow - Can I Call You Tonight?

(Lyrics):
[Verse 1]
I feel close
Well, maybe I'm not, heaven knows
It's a spotlight stuck on the ceiling
Why are these the things that I'm feeling?
There's so much time
For me to speak up, but I keep quiet
I'll complicate the most of the mantra
The power's out and I can't turn the fan on

[Chorus]
So can I call you tonight?
I'm trying to make up my mind
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real?
I hear your voice on the phone
Now I'm no longer alone
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real anymore?
'Cause I wouldn't know

[Verse 2]
Voice so low
Sneaking around, so it goes
I always try my best to listen
Picking up things that I can fidget
Circle speed
Pacing around, watching my feet
Batteries drain, I get the memo
"I think that I might have to let you go"

[Chorus]
So can I call you tonight?
I'm trying to make up my mind
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real?
I hear your voice on the phone
Now I'm no longer alone
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real anymore?
'Cause I wouldn't know

[Bridge]
(We're sorry; you have reached a number that has been disconnected or is no longer in service)
(If you feel you have reached this recording in error, please check the number and try your call again)
Don't go, don't go so easy
Don't go, don't go and leave me
Don't go, don't go so easy
Don't go, don't go and leave me
Don't go, don't go so easy
Don't go, don't go and leave me
Don't go, don't go so easy
Don't go, go

[Chorus]
So can I call you tonight?
I'm trying to make up my mind
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real?
I hear your voice on the phone
Now I'm no longer alone
Just how I feel
Could you tell me what's real anymore?
'Cause I wouldn't know

[Outro]
(Yeah, I wouldn't know)
(I wouldn't know)
(Yeah, I wouldn't know)
(Just how I feel)
(I wouldn't know)

Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX â€” interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: *NSYNC - This I Promise You (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
*NSYNC - This I Promise You
Get:

Lyrics:

[Intro: Justin]
Oh, oh, oh, oh
Oh, ooh

[Verse 1: Justin]
When the visions around you
Bring tears to your eyes
And all that surrounds you
Are secrets and lies
I'll be your strength
I'll give you hope
Keeping your faith when it's gone
The one you should call
Was standing there all along

[Chorus: All & Justin]
And I will take you in my arms
And hold you right where you belong
'Til the day my life is through
This, I promise you
This, I promise you

[Verse 2: JC & All]
I've loved you forever
In lifetimes before
And I promise you never
Will you hurt anymore
I give you my word
I give you my heart (Give you my heart)
This is a battle we've won
And with this vow
Forever has now begun

[Chorus: All, Justin & JC]
Just close your eyes (Close your eyes)
Each loving day (Each loving day)
I know this feeling won't go away (No)
'Til the day my life is through
This, I promise you
This, I promise you...

[Bridge: JC & All]
Over and over, I fall...
(Over and over, I fall)
When I hear you call
Without you in my life, baby
I just wouldn't be living at all

[Chorus: All & JC]
And I will take you in my arms
(I will take you in my arms)
And hold you right where you belong
(Right where you belong)
'Til the day my life is through
This, I promise you, babe
Just close your eyes
Each loving day (Each loving day)
I know this feeling won't go away (No)
Every word I say is true
This, I promise you
[Outro: Justin]
Every word I say is true
This, I promise you
Ooh, I promise you...

Yeah yeah yeah yeah

Ecstasy In The Palace

Hitman sipping wine

Focused on real bread unlike you loafers

I went past the snakes now I'm alone king cobra
Ooh

I need more in my life I got dough on my mind

Tryna living it up

Smoking Hollywood

There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
